"Allow others to select objects from this schema" is translated as "Allow other _users_ to select objects from this schema". The source is confusing however in my understanding, this "others" should be translated as "other object schemas".

ref: https://community.atlassian.com/t5/Jira-Service-Management-articles/Is-there-a-template-for-Insight-Cloud/ba-p/1668756
{quote}
Note: you must go to object schema > configure > general and check the box to 'Allow others to select objects from this schema' to enable other object schemas to see this schema.
{quote}

